layout.house_prompt: A cozy guest cottage with a bedroom, a sitting area, and a bathroom. The bedroom has a bed with a nightstand and a lamp on top. The sitting area has two armchairs and a wooden bookshelf full of books. A skull sits on the bookshelf. The bathroom has a toilet and a sink.

living_room.text_description: A cozy cottage sitting area with two armchairs and a wooden bookshelf full of books; a skull sits on the bookshelf. Warm, inviting rustic decor.

bedroom.text_description: A cozy cottage bedroom with a bed, a nightstand, and a lamp on top of the nightstand. Warm, calm rustic decor.

bathroom.text_description: A cozy cottage bathroom with a toilet and a sink, simple and clean.

hallway.text_description: A cozy cottage micro-vestibule entry with simple hooks and a small mat; minimal rustic detailing.
